it's Ren.

13
00:01:08,100 --> 00:01:10,990
She and Miao entered General's Residence
at the same time two years ago.

14
00:01:11,159 --> 00:01:11,920
Huh?

15
00:01:12,480 --> 00:01:12,840
Yeah.

16
00:01:13,959 --> 00:01:15,959
