21
00:02:50,879 --> 00:02:51,560
Hey.

22
00:02:51,719 --> 00:02:52,599
What's wrong?

23
00:02:52,879 --> 00:02:54,039
Are you feeling unwell?

24
00:02:56,599 --> 00:02:57,639
I'm fine.

25
00:02:58,759 --> 00:02:59,800
Master.

26
00:03:00,479 --> 00:03:01,639
I'm afraid

27
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:04,879
I won't be able to serve you anymore.

28
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:18,759
This spring water

29
00:03:18,759 --> 00:03:21,439
can cure you because of the blessing power

30
00:03:21,879 --> 00:03:24,039
given by Azure Dragon's Essence.

31
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:25,719
However,

32
00:03:26,039 --> 00:03:27,960
you're currently too weak.

33
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:30,080
The spring water alone

34
00:03:30,599 --> 00:03:31,800
